I confused the first time I played the game. my money was running low quickly and I restart the game several times because my school is bankrupt just for several days in game. then I figured out how to get past the crisis:
1. do 'to-do' lists;
2. only accepts grants that you 100% sure you can complete it quickly. otherwise, dont accept grants;
3. be patient. dont build facility you dont need yet;
4. save some cashes, build a facility u need, repeat.
